trans-unit.source: Represents a user annotation in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_caf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-caf-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Representerer en bruker merknad i den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_caf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-caf-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Annotation represents a single annotation with all associated anchoring and content data.
trans-unit.target: Merknaden representerer en enkelt merknaden alle tilknyttede forankring og innhold data.

trans-unit.source: An annotation consists of the following main elements.
trans-unit.target: Merknaden består av følgende primære elementer.

trans-unit.source: - Zero, one, or more <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A> that identify what is being annotated.
trans-unit.target: -Null, ett eller flere <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>som identifiserer det merkes som.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Zero, one, or more <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> that contain the user data for the annotation.
trans-unit.target: -Null, ett eller flere <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A>som inneholder brukerdata for merknaden.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Zero, one, or more <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Authors%2A> that define who created the annotation.
trans-unit.target: -Null, ett eller flere <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Authors%2A>som definerer hvem som har opprettet en merknad.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Authors%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.CreationTime%2A> that specifies the date and time when the annotation was created.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.CreationTime%2A>som angir datoen og klokkeslettet da merknaden ble opprettet.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.CreationTime%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.LastModificationTime%2A> that specifies when the annotation was last updated.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.LastModificationTime%2A>som angir når merknaden sist ble oppdatert.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.LastModificationTime%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A unique annotation <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Id%2A> (a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_guid](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: – En unik merknad <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Id%2A>(en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_guid](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Id%2A>

trans-unit.target: Datoen og klokkeslettet merknaden sist ble endret.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an anchor is added, removed, or modified in the list of annotation <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors*>.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når forankring legges til, fjerne eller endres i listen over merknad <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors*>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors*>

trans-unit.source: In addition to when an anchor is added or removed, AnchorChanged occurs on any modifications to an anchor subpart, such as a change to a <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart>.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til når forankring legges til eller fjernet, oppstår AnchorChanged på eventuelle endringer i en ankeret underordnet del, for eksempel en endring i en <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.ContentLocatorPart>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of zero or more <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"></xref> anchor elements that define the data selection(s) being annotated.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med null eller flere <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"> </xref> forankrer elementer som definerer data-utvalget er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource> in the Anchors collection identifies a data selection to which the annotation is bound (in other words, "the data selection that is being annotated").
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>i ankrene samlingen identifiserer en data merknaden er bundet til (altså "datautvalget merkes som").</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>

trans-unit.source: While most annotations refer to a single data selection and contain just one anchor <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>, multiple anchors can occur if a single annotation refers to multiple data selections.
trans-unit.target: Mens de fleste merknader referere til et enkelt utvalg inneholder bare én ankeret <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>, flere ankre kan oppstå hvis en enkelt merknad refererer til flere data valg.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>

trans-unit.source: The returned Anchors collection is never null; however, the collection may contain zero elements.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen returnerte ankre er aldri null. samlingen inneholder imidlertid ingen elementer.

trans-unit.source: A collection of zero or more <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"></xref> anchor elements.
trans-unit.target: En samling med null eller flere <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"> </xref> forankrer elementer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> of the annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>av merknadstypen.</xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>

trans-unit.source: The returned annotation type is the <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> name passed as a parameter to the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Merknadstypen returnerte er den <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>navnet sendes som en parameter i <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > AnnotationType returns `null` if the annotation was incorrectly constructed by using a default constructor without parameters.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > AnnotationType returnerer `null` hvis merknaden ble konstruert feil ved hjelp av en standardkonstruktør uten parametere.

trans-unit.source: (The default constructor without parameters does not fully initialize the instance and is used only internally in combination with XML serialization.) To create a new annotation, applications should use the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A> constructor that takes an <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: (Standardkonstruktør uten parametere ikke fullstendig initialisert forekomsten og brukes bare internt i kombinasjon med XML-serialisering.) Hvis du vil opprette en ny merknad programmer skal bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør som bruker en <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>som en parameter.</xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The XML qualified name for this kind of annotation.
trans-unit.target: I XML-kvalifisert navn for denne typen merknad.

trans-unit.target: Forekommer når en forfatter legges til, fjerne eller endres i listen over merknad <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Authors*>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Authors*>

trans-unit.source: To be added.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of zero or more author strings that identify who created the <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med null eller flere Forfatter strenger som identifisere hvem som har opprettet i <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The returned Authors collection is never `null`; however, the collection can contain zero elements if no author is specified.
trans-unit.target: Den returnerte forfattere-samlingen er aldri `null`; imidlertid samlingen kan inneholde null hvis ingen Forfatter er angitt.

trans-unit.source: A collection of zero or more author strings.
trans-unit.target: En samling med null eller flere Forfatter strenger.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when a cargo is added, removed, or modified in the list of annotation <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos*>.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når en gods er lagt til, fjernet eller endres i listen over merknad <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos*>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos*>

trans-unit.source: In addition to when a cargo is added or removed, CargoChanged occurs on any modification to a cargo subpart, such as a change to an <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> in the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.Contents%2A> collection of a cargo.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til når en gods legges til eller fjernet, oppstår CargoChanged på endringer i en gods underordnet del, for eksempel en endring i en <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>i den <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.Contents%2A>samling av en gods.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.Contents%2A> </xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of zero or more <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"></xref> cargo elements that contain data for the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med null eller flere <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"> </xref> gods elementer som inneholder data for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource> in the Cargos collection contains user-defined data for the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>i Cargos samlingen inneholder brukerdefinert datatype for merknaden.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource>

trans-unit.source: The returned Cargos collection is never null; however, the collection may contain zero elements if there is no user data for the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Den returnerte Cargos-samlingen er ikke null. samlingen kan imidlertid ikke inneholde elementer null hvis det er ingen brukerdata for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A collection of zero or more <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"></xref> cargo elements.
trans-unit.target: En samling med null eller flere <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource"> </xref> gods elementer.
